parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Corrosion of Rear Trailing Arms and Control Arms
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the rear trailing arms and control arms can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
